<view class="container">
  <image src="http://localhost:5001/images/recipe/05.jpg" class="recipe-image" mode="aspectFill" />
  <view class="recipe-info">
    <text class="recipe-title">切片涮肉</text>

    <view class="section-block">
      <view class="section-header">
        <view class="section-bar"></view>
        <text class="section-title">所需食材</text>
      </view>
      <view class="ing-list">
        <view class="ing-item"><text class="ing-dot"></text><text class="ing-name">成品火锅底料</text></view>
        <view class="ing-item"><text class="ing-dot"></text><text class="ing-name">姜片</text></view>
        <view class="ing-item"><text class="ing-dot"></text><text class="ing-name">葱段</text></view>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="section-block">
      <view class="section-header">
        <view class="section-bar"></view>
        <text class="section-title">烹饪步骤</text>
      </view>
      <view class="step-list">
        <view class="step-item">
          <view class="step-num"><text>1</text></view>
          <text class="step-text">使用成品火锅底料，加入适量清水或高汤，放入姜片、葱段，开火煮沸。</text>
        </view>
        <view class="step-item">
          <view class="step-num"><text>2</text></view>
          <text class="step-text">待锅底烧开，放入切好的羊肉卷片涮熟即可。</text>
        </view>
        <view class="step-item">
          <view class="step-num"><text>3</text></view>
          <text class="step-text">可根据个人口味搭配蘸料食用。</text>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>